[
    {
        "source_sentence": "父子合集經卷第十七",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試鴻臚卿宣梵大師賜紫",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門臣日稱等奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "六界差別品第二十六之二",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c26_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，聞妙樂聲，心生適悅。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中美妙音樂，是實有不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c28_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有樂聲，何況復有生適悅耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a02_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生聞可意聲起於愛樂，而生染著，造作惡行，身三、語四、意業三種，作是業已剎那滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，最後邊際命根滅時，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時無所從來，滅無所去；彼業生時無所從來，滅無所去；初識生時無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，了知業轉無有作者，亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳聞惡聲則生憂惱，如人夢中親愛別離，悲號啼哭，生大苦惱。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已憶夢中事，是實有不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，為智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中親愛畢竟無有，何況復有別離事耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生聞其惡聲，則生憂惱，起於瞋心，造作瞋業，所謂身三、語四、意業三種，造彼業已剎那滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，最後邊際命根滅時，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b02_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿修羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b02_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b06_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b07_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時無所從來，滅無所去；彼業生時無所從來，滅無所去；初識生時無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b07_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b09_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b10_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知業轉無有作者亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b11_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b13_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳聞捨聲起於捨想，如人夢中聞他宣說不了義句。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b13_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已憶念夢中所聞之聲，為實有不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b16_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有音聲，何況更有不了義句。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生耳聞捨聲，不達義趣，輕慢毀呰，造作癡業。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身三、語四、意三種業，最初造作，即便滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，最後邊際命根滅時，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺憶夢中聞不了義句。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b21_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b28_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時無所從來，滅無所去；彼業生時無所從來，滅無所去；初識生時無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c02_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c03_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知業轉無有作者，亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c04_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c07_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；空無空相，名無相解脫門；若無有相，則無願求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是三法與空共行，涅盤先道決定，如法界周遍虛空際，於此譬喻當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，以旃檀香或多摩羅葉香及餘香等而以塗身。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中所塗之香，是實有不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，為智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
