    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶其夢中食苦瓠等，為實有不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c21_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c21_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無苦瓠等，況復食耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c22_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c24_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c24_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生夢為饑逼，噉其苦味，心生恚惱，造是業行，身三、語四、意三種行，造彼業已即便滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，最後邊際命根滅時，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968c29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a02_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a05_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a05_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a05_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時，無所從來，滅無所去；彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所去；初識生時，無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知業轉無有作者亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人夢中舌根斷壞。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a12_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中，是為實不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王曰：「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a14_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有舌根，況復斷壞？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a16_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生見舌壞已，心生恚惱造是業行，身三、語四、意三種業，造彼業已，剎那滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業不依四方四維上下而住，最後邊際命根滅謝，自分業報皆悉現前，如夢覺已，念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時，無所從來，滅無所去；彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所去；初識生時，無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969a29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知業轉無有作者亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969b01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；空無空相，名無相解脫門；若無有相，則無願求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是三法，與空共行，涅盤先道，決定如法界，周遍虛空際；於此譬喻，當如是知。」",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "父子合集經卷第十七",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0969b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
